== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
void TTF_SetFontKerning(TTF_Font *font, int allowed);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''font'''
|[[TTF_Font]] handle
|-
